<div class="container">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container-fluid" >
    	<div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-left: 50%; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 5%">
    		<a class="topLevel text" href="/createRoom" id="createRoom" ><span class="text-center raise boxed headertext text">Create</span></a>
    		<img id="leftaux" src="/static/images/leftaux.svg" class="img-responsive animated slideInRight" style="position: sticky; margin-top: 10%;">
    	</div>
    		<br><br>
    	<h2 class="text middle">OR</h2>
    		<br><br>
    		<div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-right: 50%; margin-left: auto;">
    			<img id="rightaux" style="position: sticky;" class="img-responsive text animated slideInLeft" src="/static/images/rightaux.svg" alt="">
    			<a class="standard-text" href="/getRooms" id="joinRoom"><span class="text-center raise boxed text headertext"><span class="text headertext" style="opacity: 0">1</span>Join<span class="text headertext" style="opacity: 0">1</span></span></a>
    		</div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="exampleModalLong" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLongTitle" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header"  style="background-color: #1E1D1D">
        <h5 class="modal-title text headertext" id="exampleModalLongTitle">Welcome to Auxen</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body" style="background-color: #1E1D1D">
        <p class="text">
          Auxen is a real-time music sharing application. It's pretty simple. You can choose to create a room.
          You're now the DJ for the room you just created. You then start playing music like you normally do.
          People can join the room and you can see all the users who joined. Whoever joins will automatically
          have their music set to whatever you, the DJ, are playing. If you join a room, your music will be set to
          whatever the DJ is currently playing. You can leave the room to take control of your music again.
       </p>
       <img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/TsxMkIKHpvFaU/giphy.gif" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer" style="background-color: #1E1D1D">
        <h1 type="button" class="text small boxed raise" data-dismiss="modal">Get started</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript" src="/static/scripts/modal.js"></script>
<script>
  $(document).ready(function() {
    var spotifyId = '{{spotifyId}}';
    var imageURL = '{{imageURL}}'
    var username = '{{username}}'
    localStorage.setItem("spotifyId", spotifyId);
    localStorage.setItem("imageURL", imageURL);
    localStorage.setItem("username", username);
  })
</script>
